ZH: 他一直秉持着正直的品德。
EN: He has always maintained upright moral character.

ZH: 她秉持信念，不断努力追求梦想。
EN: She holds on to her beliefs and continually strives to pursue her dreams.

ZH: 这家公司一直秉持质量第一的原则。
EN: This company has always adhered to the principle of quality first.

ZH: 学校一直秉持严格管理，确保学生安全。
EN: The school has always maintained strict management to ensure student safety.

ZH: 她秉持爱心，乐于帮助他人。
EN: She embraces compassion and is willing to help others.

ZH: 这位领导一直秉持公平公正的态度处理问题。
EN: This leader has always handled issues with fairness and justice.

ZH: 团队成员们一直秉持团结合作的精神。
EN: The team members have always maintained the spirit of unity and cooperation.

ZH: 我们要秉持诚实守信的原则做人。
EN: We should abide by the principle of honesty and integrity in our actions.

ZH: 这部电影秉持着牢固的历史事实。
EN: This film adheres to solid historical facts.

ZH: 他秉持着乐观的态度面对挑战。
EN: He maintains an optimistic attitude towards challenges.

